r runner to compete at theParalympicsas she took part in the women's athletics programme atParis 2024.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy notice\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 411}, {\"ngram\": \"Valentina Petrillo\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 430}, {\"ngram\": \"the first transgender runner\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 466}, {\"ngram\": \"theParalympicsas\", \"from\": 481, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's athletics programme\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 546}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Petrillo,who transitioned in 2019,is a visually impaired runner and competes in the T12 200m and 400m sprints.\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 673, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Petrillo\", \"from\": 563, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"2019,is\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 599}, {\"ngram\": \"a visually impaired runner\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"competes\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"the T12 200m and 400m sprints\", \"from\": 643, \"to\": 672}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She finished second in her 400m heat at the Stade de France on Monday morning and will run in the semi-finals at around 8pm BST, with the medal race scheduled for Tuesday.\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 798, \"end\": 801, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"score\": 0.9999999398346535, \"rank\": 6.016516257087453e-08, \"text\": \"BST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Summer_Time\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her 400m heat\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 710}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday morning\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 751}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal race\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 822}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 50-year-old was initially reported to be the first openly transgender Paralympian.\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 921, \"end\": 932, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Dutch athlete Ingrid van Kranen finished ninth in the women's discus final at the Rio 2016 Games.\", \"from\": 934, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.8015591547655754, \"rank\": 0.1454924712731671, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Rio 2016 Games\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Petrillo previously won 11 national titles in the men's category as a married father of two, and her participation at these Games has caused controversy.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Petrillo\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"11 national titles\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1084}, {\"ngram\": \"the men's category\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1106}, {\"ngram\": \"a married father\", \"from\": 1110, \"to\": 1126}, {\"ngram\": \"her participation\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1156}, {\"ngram\": \"these Games\", \"from\": 1160, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"controversy\", \"from\": 1183, \"to\": 1194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From today I do not want to hear anything more about discrimination, prejudices against transgender people,\\\" she said after her heat.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1331, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 1203, \"to\": 1208}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"discrimination\", \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"transgender people\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"her heat\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1330}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are lots of people dying only for being trans, people are killed because they are trans, people commit suicide because they are trans and lose their jobs, or (they are) are not included in sport.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 1343, \"to\": 1347}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"trans\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1428, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"suicide\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1449}, {\"ngram\": \"trans\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"their jobs\", \"from\": 1482, \"to\": 1492}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I made it.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I can make it, everyone can make it.\\\"\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Petrillo said before the Games that she had learnt to deal with \\\"jealousy\\\" and has \\\"nothing to fear\\\" after concerns about her inclusion were raised by fellow athletes, includingrival T12 runner Katrin Mueller-Rottgardt.\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1811, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1775, \"end\": 1778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thoracic_vertebrae\", \"score\": 0.9999859633820211, \"rank\": 1.4028258307059018e-05, \"text\": \"T12\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\", \"Q265868\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thoracic_vertebrae\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thoracic_vertebrae\"}, {\"begin\": 1786, \"end\": 1810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katrin_Mueller-Rottgardt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Katrin Mueller-Rottgardt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katrin_Mueller-Rottgardt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Katrin_Mueller-Rottgardt\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Petrillo\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1600}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1622}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"jealousy\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1665}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1676, \"to\": 1683}, {\"ngram\": \"concerns\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"her inclusion\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"fellow athletes\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, I can not wait to be in Paris and race on that beautiful purple track and in front of all that enthusiastic crowd,\\\" Petrillo toldSpanish sports websiteRelevo.\", \"from\": 1813, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1848, \"end\": 1853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999752681109, \"rank\": 2.473173982044893e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that beautiful purple track\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1906}, {\"ngram\": \"all that enthusiastic crowd\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"toldSpanish sports\", \"from\": 1949, \"to\": 1967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think there will be a lot more love for me than I can imagine.\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 2048, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot more love\", \"from\": 2006, \"to\": 2021}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's only fair that each of us can express ourselves in our own gender.\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2079, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"our own gender\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sport should teach us the value of inclusion and this is fundamental for people's happiness.\\\"\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2144}, {\"ngram\": \"the value\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2154}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 2158, \"to\": 2167}, {\"ngram\": \"people's happiness\", \"from\": 2196, \"to\": 2214}]}, {\"sentence\": \"German athlete Mueller-Rottgardt suggested 200m opponent Petrillo, who won two bronze medals at last year's World Para Athletics Championships, has a physical advantage due to having \\\"lived and trained as a man\\\".\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2430, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2218, \"end\": 2224, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.989770903498269, \"rank\": 0.007130795771995306, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2326, \"end\": 2360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Para_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999865884063965, \"rank\": 1.3387346572777071e-05, \"text\": \"World Para Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Para_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Para_Athletics_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"200m opponent Petrillo\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"two bronze medals\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2310}, {\"ngram\": \"a physical advantage\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2386}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Basically, everyone should live in everyday life the way they feel comfortable, but I find it difficult in competitive sports,\\\" said Mueller-Rottgardt.\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2584, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2452}, {\"ngram\": \"everyday life\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2481}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive sports\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2558}, {\"ngram\": \"Mueller-Rottgardt\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2583}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Petrillo has lived and trained as a man for a long time, so there is a possibility that the physical requirements are different to those of someone who was born as a woman.\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Petrillo\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2594}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2625}, {\"ngram\": \"a long time\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"a possibility\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2668}, {\"ngram\": \"the physical requirements\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2699}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2733}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This could give an advantage.\\\"\", \"from\": 2759, \"to\": 2789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an advantage\", \"from\": 2775, \"to\": 2787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Round one of the women's T12 400m is scheduled for Monday 2 September at Stade de France, with the final the following day.\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the women's T12\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2819}, {\"ngram\": \"400m\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2824}, {\"ngram\": \"Monday\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2848}, {\"ngram\": \"2 September\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"Stade de France\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2879}, {\"ngram\": \"the final the following day\", \"from\": 2886, \"to\": 2913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 200m races take place on 6-7 September at the same venue.\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2976, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 200m races\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2929}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"6-7 September\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2957}, {\"ngram\": \"the same venue\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2975}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have learned to let go of what I cannot control,\\\" continued Petrillo.\", \"from\": 2978, \"to\": 3050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Petrillo\", \"from\": 3041, \"to\": 3049}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am now psychologically stronger than I was some time ago and this is also due to the support of my psychologist.\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3166, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the support\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3146}, {\"ngram\": \"my psychologist\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People always criticise, for whatever reason and that is why in my case, they are even more likely to do so.\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3173}, {\"ngram\": \"whatever reason\", \"from\": 3196, \"to\": 3211}, {\"ngram\": \"my case\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3238}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I gradually understood that you have to live with people's envy and jealousy, unfortunately.\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3370, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people's envy\", \"from\": 3328, \"to\": 3341}, {\"ngram\": \"jealousy\", \"from\": 3346, \"to\": 3354}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But, for my part, I am aware that what I do is real and therefore I have nothing to fear.\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my part\", \"from\": 3380, \"to\": 3387}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 3444, \"to\": 3451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am absolutely aware of the social and cultural value of my presence in Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3